RunWorkflowRequest.description:
Request to run a workflow with input documents and/or JSON.

Documents are provided as a dict mapping start node IDs to document inputs.
JSON inputs are provided as a dict mapping start_json node IDs to JSON data.

Example:
    {
        "documents": {
            "start-node-1": {
                "filename": "invoice.pdf",
                "mime_type": "application/pdf",
                "content": "base64_encoded_content..."
            }
        },
        "json_inputs": {
            "start-json-node-1": {
                "customer_name": "John Doe",
                "invoice_number": "INV-001"
            }
        },
    }
